data.title: Steve Bisley Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about Steve Bisley on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature Steve Bisley including Mad Max, The Great Gatsby, and more.
data.text:
One for the Social Workers

Goldie and substitute partner Jack Christey take on surveillance duty to catch a rapist who has been abducting women from parked cars and assaulting them.

Heads or Tales

Detectives Goldstein and Christey investigate when a gym bag containing a man's severed head is found washed up on a beach.

Watery Grave

Holloway and Blakemore investigate the disappearance of an environmental activist who they believe is responsible for an explosive protest that put one man in hospital. Sykes tries to determine what happened to a triathlon competitor who vanished during a race.
